        <span class="token class-name">PageInfo</span><span class="token generics"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">Publish</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> pageInfo <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>quanZiApi<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">queryPublishList</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>user<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getId</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> page<span class="token punctuation">,</span> pageSize<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
        
       <span class="token comment">//。。。。代码略。。。。。</span>

        <span class="token keyword">return</span> pageResult<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>需要注意的是，在APP中，如果请求响应401，会跳转到登录页面。</p>
